WEBVTT

00:01.233 --> 00:03.077
Could you call me a taxi, please?

00:03.197 --> 00:04.110
Yes, of course!

00:04.268 --> 00:04.852
Where to?

00:05.321 --> 00:06.567
To Paddington Station.

00:06.839 --> 00:08.098
And when would you like it for?

00:08.388 --> 00:09.361
Now, please.

00:29.155 --> 00:30.319
How much is it?

00:30.571 --> 00:33.181
That's 13.60, please.

00:39.138 --> 00:42.881
Make it 15 pounds, and could I have a receipt?

00:43.397 --> 00:44.525
Thank you very much, madam.

00:55.027 --> 00:57.887
Could I have a ticket to Heathrow Airport, please?

00:58.073 --> 00:59.168
Single or return?

00:59.695 --> 01:00.662
Single, please.

01:01.095 --> 01:02.909
Standard or first class?

01:03.057 --> 01:04.343
Standard, please.

01:05.607 --> 01:07.178
That's 18 pounds.

01:07.768 --> 01:09.037
Can I pay by credit card?

01:09.214 --> 01:10.035
Yes, of course.

